  "comment": "LUCID 2.4 LED BAR 4x 30W RGBW: The LUCID is equipped with 4 or 8 high power COB LEDs that can be used for either wash effects or as a pixel controlled bar. With the latest COB technology it's possible to create flawless RGBW colour mixing. The LUCID can either be used in stand-alone mode and run its preset programs in a certain speed or follows the music, thanks to the built-in microphone. But for full control you can also use a DMX controller to program this light effect into your shows. The LUCID can be placed on the floor by turning the bracket upside down, making it ideal for both fixed installations and rental.",
